      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA FLAMING (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Richmond behind Live And Free (18.92) in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Top prospect. DIRE (7) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.87) in a Grade 4/5 at Richmond. Has a good record at this journey. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. SANCTIMONIOUS (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing seventh (23.86) last time in a Grade 5 at Gosford. Has good speed and a low draw is a big help. Has ability and is one of the better chances. TILLY'S ON TOP (3) should be thereabouts.",
